Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.92,0:01:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.29,0:01:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiyori is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.01,0:01:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.54,0:01:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven years ago on that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.56,0:02:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...the meteorite that fell on \NEarth dried up the oceans.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,From the meteorite an alien \Nspecies, the Worms, were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The secret organization ZECT \Ndeveloped the Masked Rider System.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They joined to be warriors that fight the Worms.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.21,0:02:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Riders calling themselves Neo-ZECT have \Nappeared who want to revolt against the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:39.47,YearsLater - Copy,Blue text,760,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\fnCalibri\fs52\bord0\\i1\c&H805931&}7 Years Later - The Present
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:59.05,Default - Up,Newspaper,0,0,0,,'Worm Menace'
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't push!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.53,0:03:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I said wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.61,0:03:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there.{Wait a moment.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,ZECT and Neo-ZECT's dispute is still continuing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.14,0:03:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The path I walk... is for me to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.72,0:04:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I can't see behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No good! There are too many!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.68,0:04:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I have a lot too! We can't run any further!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oda!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nowhere left to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only remnants of Neo-ZECT.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's to win our freedom, \Nthen we'll fight to the last man!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,ZECT doesn't allow traitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.04,0:05:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll follow you to the very edge\N of the land and eliminate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.17,0:05:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are just scared of freedom, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind is fickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It just flows wherever it wishes to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all you want to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please just wait a second!{Please wait a moment!}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.46,0:06:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Our goal is to defeat the Worms!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Not for Riders to fight each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.89,0:06:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've begged on my knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Return to ZECT.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I will endure any humiliation\N if it accomplishes that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:07:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What we Neo-ZECT hate the most\N is being ordered around like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then by my hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...I will smash your rotten guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.09,0:07:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you should have \Nsaid in the first place, ZECT dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.82,0:07:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:34.28,Belt,,0,0,0,,TRANSFORM
