Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.74,0:09:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandmother once said...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,"I am, the man who walks the path of heaven..."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,"...the man who will rule over everything"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.77,0:09:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tendou... Souji.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:51.78,Belt,,0,0,0,,TRANSFORM
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Cast Off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.07,0:09:59.42,Belt,,0,0,0,,CAST OFF
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:02.91,Belt,,0,0,0,,CHANGE BEETLE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.44,0:10:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,An unpleasant note that \Ndisrupts Perfect Harmony!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How unlikeable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wants to pay for my strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I come at a high cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.98,0:10:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I, the sun, shines!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oda.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really joining with that Tendou guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.24,0:11:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that guy interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.49,0:11:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How so? Isn't he just arrogant?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But that strength is real.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.25,0:11:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a darkness in his \Neyes that draws me to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.00,0:11:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I don't know what that darkness is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.56,0:12:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami Arata, pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been going out with her for a year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That... hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't do it, she won't \Nstay with you. Go on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go...{I'm going...}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiyori.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.37,0:12:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I... want to always join in battery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the battery in your bike broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,By battery I mean a pitcher and catcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.34,0:12:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,With me... will you m...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,M- M- M- Ma-
Comment: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,M-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.08,0:13:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.17,0:13:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.44,0:13:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Real mackerel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to eat that.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.82,0:13:16.10,Default,,0,0,60,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.13,0:13:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No one would give you mackerel to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,M- M-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.90,0:13:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,M-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.92,0:13:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please make your mackerel miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandmother once said...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.56,0:13:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me. We have to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you joining with Oda?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.88,0:13:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.53,0:13:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a surprisingly good price.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.01,0:14:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Neo-ZECT say it's for freedom, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...they're just thugs doing whatever they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandmother once said...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,"The strong are saved, the weak crumble."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.76,0:14:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the strong need to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.29,0:14:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That only the strong should survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the law of evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... I'm out, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.28,0:14:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiyori!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.52,0:14:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a bit tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.21,0:14:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.49,0:15:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm joining with Oda to\N destroy Neo-ZECT from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,To do that I need your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So you told him about the \NLadder to Heaven project?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.65,0:15:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we trust this Tendou man?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.92,0:15:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not like we can hide this info.\N At least this way we can use him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.22,0:15:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Use him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We feed Neo-ZECT information to control them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.57,0:15:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't just decide that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:16:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to recommend you as the one to\N carry out the Ladder to Heaven project.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ladder to Heaven project\N will decide humanity's fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.62,0:16:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We must not let it be interrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I have another ace up my sleeve{trump card}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.56,0:16:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.86,0:16:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ladder to Heaven project?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.37,0:16:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.92,0:16:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If that succeeds, humanity will\N be able to regain its oceans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we regain our oceans?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The orbital elevator connecting the\N land to space is already complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,From there they create a\N phase in space somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.52,0:17:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And draw a comet to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.26,0:17:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A comet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Comets are masses of ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.93,0:17:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If successful, we will obtain\N a great deal of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.98,0:17:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.85,0:17:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If that happens, ZECT will gain even more power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why doesn't Neo-ZECT take over that project?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.54,0:17:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Our offensive capability is\N like a whirlwind facing a storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Better to remain as a fickle wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.78,0:17:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fed up with a life of just running!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.14,0:17:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're serious about being free...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...then we have to stand on top of ZECT.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:18:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go obtain data on ZECT's \Noffensive capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They say "those who control \Nthe water, control the world".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You changed the phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's you, then you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.37,0:18:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's decided, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.10,0:18:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.34,0:19:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The story that ZECT has a pet gold Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.01,0:19:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems those who fight \Nhim lose before they start.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Already lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all that can be said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,When we find them, all that's left are \Nthe corpses of his opponents and rose petals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why ask that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.09,0:19:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's the strongest one, then I want to duel him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an interesting guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.56,0:21:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the only place where\N I have memories of my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.70,0:21:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.28,0:21:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If the oceans are restored, \NI'm sure life will be peaceful, like in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.94,0:21:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you with me, Hiyori.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.52,0:21:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,By my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.16,0:22:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.58,0:22:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.85,0:22:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiyori, I bet you're cold too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get your coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.13,0:22:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.88,0:22:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.76,0:22:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually really happy about how Arata feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.21,0:22:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.52,0:23:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Arata...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.77,0:23:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Arata!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.21,0:23:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.73,0:23:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.72,0:23:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.09,0:23:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.04,0:23:26.05,Belt,,0,0,0,,TRANSFORM
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.65,0:23:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Cast Off!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.91,0:23:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.25,0:23:54.78,Belt,,0,0,0,,RIDER KICK
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.40,0:24:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiyori?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.26,0:24:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiyori!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.47,0:24:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiyori...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.33,0:24:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiyori!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.78,0:24:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiyori!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.96,0:24:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiyori...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.86,0:24:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.90,0:24:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.32,0:24:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Take her to a hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.90,0:24:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Go call them!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.93,0:25:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...{Sir...}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.32,0:25:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.40,0:25:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiyori doesn't have much time left{only has a small period of time left}?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.88,0:25:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unfortunate. It's the result of the\N meteorite from seven years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.58,0:25:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I told Hiyori, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.72,0:25:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... Hiyori knew all along{that}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.88,0:25:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor{Sir}! That's much too tragic!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.89,0:25:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Please heal her!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.46,0:25:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She... lost her parents because of that meteorite!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.69,0:25:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{This time}Now she will lose her life too!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.89,0:26:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.10,0:26:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...heal her.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.64,0:26:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiyori is... here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.04,0:26:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.60,0:26:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.24,0:26:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.33,0:27:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oda has taken the information you gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.85,0:27:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They're planning to take over\N the Ladder to Heaven project.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.20,0:27:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.70,0:27:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.72,0:27:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If I lose Hiyori...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.82,0:27:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.04,0:28:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic man.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.52,0:28:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you protect Hiyori like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.40,0:28:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I will crush Neo-ZECT.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.10,0:28:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys make the Ladder \Nto Heaven project succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.12,0:28:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is to protect Hiyori as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.45,0:28:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard how they're going \Nto make the phase dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.48,0:28:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.58,0:28:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a giant Clock Up machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.97,0:29:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,To use that they have to send a Rider up\N the orbital elevator to the space station.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.17,0:29:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't believe that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.46,0:29:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in communication with ZECT.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.81,0:29:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw him with Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.69,0:29:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just a source of information.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.78,0:29:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't look like that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.32,0:29:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretending to be with us so\N you can crush us with the organization, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.58,0:29:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I get if I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.01,0:29:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll beat all the excuses out\N of your body that I'll need.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.02,0:29:55.20,Default,italics,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hiyori...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.33,0:30:02.30,Default,italics,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it be because you're sick...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.24,0:30:04.98,Default,italics,0,0,0,,{\i1}...that you turned down my proposal?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.10,0:30:10.62,Default,italics,0,0,0,,I don't care about that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.25,0:30:16.21,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Let's overcome your sickness together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.61,0:30:21.94,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Thank you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.00,0:30:27.08,Default,italics,0,0,0,,But... that's really enough.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.69,0:30:36.52,Default,italics,0,0,0,,My feelings for you are greater than all others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.25,0:30:41.50,Default,italics,0,0,0,,From now on please let me protect you, Hiyori.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.08,0:30:43.90,Default,italics,0,0,0,,No...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.40,0:30:47.05,Default,italics,0,0,0,,I will protect you, Hiyori.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.88,0:30:52.12,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Later...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.08,0:30:57.78,Default,italics,0,0,0,,...how many days will I live?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.10,0:31:02.09,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Take it day by day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.18,0:31:05.94,Default,italics,0,0,0,,We'll cherish each of them...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.86,0:31:08.60,Default,italics,0,0,0,,...together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.52,0:31:14.57,Default,italics,0,0,0,,As a family.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.04,0:31:40.05,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.96,0:31:45.69,Default,italics,0,0,0,,I'm getting sleepy. Put more vigor into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.96,0:31:49.81,Default,italics,0,0,0,,What are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.81,0:31:50.60,Default,italics,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.93,0:31:52.84,Default,italics,0,0,0,,What are you afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.64,0:31:54.84,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.25,0:32:06.20,Default,italics,0,0,0,,He might be plotting something like you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.97,0:32:11.50,Default,italics,0,0,0,,But it's surely something really big.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.22,0:32:17.16,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Is it possible to be bigger than trying to\N overtake the Ladder to Heaven project?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.10,0:32:20.68,Default,italics,0,0,0,,I want to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.18,0:32:25.48,Default,italics,0,0,0,,You sure about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.21,0:32:30.85,Default,italics,0,0,0,,I might betray you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.32,0:32:32.65,Default,italics,0,0,0,,When that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.55,0:32:35.05,Default,italics,0,0,0,,...I will deal with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.96,0:32:46.42,Default,italics,0,0,0,,The Ladder to Heaven project will\N be implemented in a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.70,0:32:51.84,Default,italics,0,0,0,,If we're to get under ZECT, we have to act now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.49,0:32:54.40,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.25,0:32:56.40,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Daisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.80,0:32:58.10,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Gather the troops!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.46,0:33:04.42,Default,italics,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.96,0:33:07.16,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.16,0:33:08.18,Default,italics,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.96,0:33:10.94,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Neo-ZECT is making their move.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.85,0:33:17.21,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Notify headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.10,0:33:18.86,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.53,0:33:25.44,Default,italics,0,0,0,,You sure you want to have\N your wedding in my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.70,0:33:26.49,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.13,0:33:30.78,Default,italics,0,0,0,,It's because I love this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.92,0:33:32.78,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.88,0:33:37.25,Default,italics,0,0,0,,I also thought this place would be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.25,0:33:38.53,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.32,0:33:40.98,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.30,0:33:44.58,Default,italics,0,0,0,,You've been chosen as the one to carry\N out the Ladder to Heaven project.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.34,0:33:46.58,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.58,0:33:47.40,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.97,0:33:49.89,Default,italics,0,0,0,,The project will be implemented now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.96,0:33:52.30,Default,italics,0,0,0,,But there are still arrangements.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.41,0:33:56.86,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Tendou has betrayed you. \NHe's sped up the timing for the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.45,0:33:58.61,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Come right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.70,0:34:02.37,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Tendou, that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.44,0:34:08.64,Default,italics,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.17,0:34:18.82,Default,italics,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I have to go right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.16,0:34:20.82,Default,italics,0,0,0,,But I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.42,0:34:25.90,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Till then... please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.48,0:34:29.64,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Have a safe trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.77,0:35:08.76,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Today...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.30,0:35:16.46,Default,italics,0,0,0,,We will... bring down the ZECT dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.85,0:35:20.82,Default,italics,0,0,0,,We're taking over the Ladder to Heaven project.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.62,0:35:23.98,Default,italics,0,0,0,,And!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.74,0:35:26.54,Default,italics,0,0,0,,We will stand at the top of humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.24,0:35:29.17,Default,italics,0,0,0,,We will be the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.09,0:35:32.60,Default,italics,0,0,0,,And for the first time obtain true freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.59,0:36:04.84,Default,italics,0,0,0,,We're nothing more than a diversion.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.08,0:36:09.62,Default,italics,0,0,0,,We're to draw off as much of the\N enemy's main force as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.70,0:36:11.97,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Women are flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.86,0:36:17.53,Default,italics,0,0,0,,If it were up to me, I would not \Nbring a flower to the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.96,0:36:23.89,Default,italics,0,0,0,,When this project is over, \Ncan you do my make up?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.24,0:36:26.58,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Be glad too.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.70,0:36:31.34,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.34,0:36:32.20,Belt,italics,0,0,0,,TRANSFORM
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.56,0:36:35.49,Default,italics,0,0,0,,I'm going on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.77,0:36:47.98,Default,italics,0,0,0,,It's begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.25,0:36:51.38,Default,italics,0,0,0,,We're going too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.57,0:37:05.26,Default,italics,0,0,0,,The two are on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.78,0:37:09.32,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Alright. Activate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.09,0:37:41.98,Default,italics,0,0,0,,No one's here. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.37,0:37:51.62,Default,italics,0,0,0,,What are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.62,0:37:56.33,Default,italics,0,0,0,,If women are flowers, \Nthen betrayal is a sweet nectar.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.48,0:37:58.60,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.40,0:38:01.85,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Wind boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.34,0:38:26.21,Default,italics,0,0,0,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.70,0:38:31.90,Default,italics,0,0,0,,...wanted to... be the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.58,0:38:33.62,Default,italics,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.00,0:39:12.93,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Was our plan leaked?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.50,0:39:21.08,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Shuda! You're a traitor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.08,0:39:24.04,Default,italics,0,0,0,,You betrayed ZECT, \Nwhat do you think you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.18,0:39:26.60,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Drake has already been executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.60,0:39:28.60,Default,italics,0,0,0,,You have no chance of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.97,0:39:31.04,Default,italics,0,0,0,,This is absolute victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.92,0:39:33.44,Default,italics,0,0,0,,A perfect mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.57,0:39:45.53,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Tendou! You head for the Ladder to Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.72,0:39:46.61,Default,italics,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.77,0:39:48.92,Default,italics,0,0,0,,I'll beat all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.92,0:39:51.82,Default,italics,0,0,0,,I control the land. You control heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.16,0:39:53.33,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.33,0:39:57.96,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Your opponent is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.10,0:39:59.72,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.24,0:40:08.26,Belt,italics,0,0,0,,TRANSFORM
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.53,0:40:18.38,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Your opponent is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.82,0:40:20.14,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Transform.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.14,0:40:21.18,Belt,italics,0,0,0,,TRANSFORM
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.26,0:40:24.98,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.38,0:40:45.65,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.34,0:40:51.16,Default,italics,0,0,0,,I'm able to have a new family.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.60,0:40:53.97,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.02,0:41:04.80,Default,italics,0,0,0,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.65,0:41:07.06,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Try it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.74,0:41:10.32,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Hiyori!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.30,0:41:17.86,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Something is approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.92,0:41:22.04,Default,italics,0,0,0,,It's Kabuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.97,0:41:26.01,Default,italics,0,0,0,,What is he trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.90,0:41:27.98,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Cast Off.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.98,0:41:29.53,Belt,italics,0,0,0,,CAST OFF
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.34,0:42:01.02,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Open.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.80,0:42:12.25,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Yo. You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.84,0:42:13.98,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Tendou...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.88,0:42:19.21,Default,italics,0,0,0,,You bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.82,0:42:23.48,Default,italics,0,0,0,,What have you come for?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.14,0:42:26.81,Default,italics,0,0,0,,There's always a hidden side to ZECT's actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.09,0:42:28.90,Default,italics,0,0,0,,I have come to crush that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.01,0:42:34.37,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Kagami... you go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.93,0:42:38.61,Default,italics,0,0,0,,I'll get rid of this maggot.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.85,0:43:05.31,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.31,0:43:06.31,Belt,italics,0,0,0,,TRANSFORM
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.31,0:43:07.18,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.18,0:43:08.31,Belt,italics,0,0,0,,TRANSFORM
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.84,0:43:27.70,Default,top,0,0,0,,Computer. The first floor is locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.10,0:43:31.01,Default,top,0,0,0,,Preparing to create a hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.56,0:43:33.14,Default - Up,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay, I've got it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.61,0:44:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Clock Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.44,0:44:25.86,Belt,,0,0,0,,CLOCK UP
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.86,0:44:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Clock Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.78,0:44:27.60,Belt,,0,0,0,,CLOCK UP
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.49,0:45:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not call the gold Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.05,0:45:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what you're after?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.85,0:45:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Clock Up Machine power on.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.89,0:46:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.42,0:46:25.85,Default - Up,Top,0,0,0,,{\i1}Emergency. Emergency.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.26,0:47:00.85,Default,Top,0,0,0,,The Ladder to Heaven \Nproject is proceeding well.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.30,0:48:25.67,Default,Top,0,0,0,,What are you trying to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.67,0:48:28.02,Default,Top,0,0,0,,If you want to live, then don't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.44,0:48:30.36,Default,Top,0,0,0,,I don't need your pity!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.36,0:48:34.30,Default,Top,0,0,0,,The flame of my passion won't lose to this heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.82,0:49:06.17,Belt,Top,0,0,0,,RIDER BEAT
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.90,0:49:32.05,Default,Top,0,0,0,,How can perfect death befall me?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.61,0:49:42.20,Default,Top,0,0,0,,We still have... Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.32,0:49:44.56,Default,Top,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.13,0:49:53.06,Default,Top,0,0,0,,My soul is with ZECT!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.53,0:49:58.16,Default,Top,0,0,0,,You lost your last ray of hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.02,0:50:00.84,Default,Top,0,0,0,,I will protect ZECT!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.84,0:50:02.00,Default,Top,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.64,0:50:04.26,Default,Top,0,0,0,,But I will crush ZECT!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.50,0:51:10.20,Default,Top,0,0,0,,A rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.82,0:51:12.90,Default,Top,0,0,0,,Are you the gold Rider?!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.54,0:51:35.88,Default,Top,0,0,0,,But I hadn't... done anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.10,0:51:41.45,Default,Top,0,0,0,,Tendou...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.26,0:51:46.46,Default,Top,0,0,0,,As long... as you're there...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.66,0:52:04.51,Default,Top,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.44,0:52:08.17,Default,Top,0,0,0,,How dare you deceive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.12,0:52:11.36,Default,Top,0,0,0,,You let yourself be deceived.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.61,0:52:13.08,Default,Top,0,0,0,,Didn't you see that meteorite?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.08,0:52:13.88,Default,Top,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.85,0:52:21.34,Default,Top,0,0,0,,Why don't you punch back?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.61,0:52:26.98,Default,Top,0,0,0,,I don't want to sadden Hiyori.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.74,0:52:29.98,Default,Top,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.65,0:52:34.66,Default,Top,0,0,0,,You also have feelings for Hiyori...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.64,0:52:45.98,Default,Top,0,0,0,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.62,0:52:51.24,Default,Top,0,0,0,,...my little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.50,0:52:58.52,Default,Top,0,0,0,,Hey! What do you mean little sister?!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.09,0:53:03.05,Default,Top,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.05,0:53:04.45,Default,italics,0,0,0,,Kagami...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.45,0:53:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hurry back.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.46,0:53:08.33,Default,Italics,0,0,0,,Hiyori is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.24,0:53:19.28,Default,Italics,0,0,0,,A meteorite is currently \Nheaded towards Earth. If it hits...{Currently a meteorite is \Nheaded towards Earth, if it hits...}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.10,0:53:23.32,Default,Italics,0,0,0,,...the Earth will be completely destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.65,0:53:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tadokoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.48,0:53:28.00,Default,Italics,0,0,0,,However, do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.96,0:53:35.45,Default,Italics,0,0,0,,The space station has antimatter\N missiles that we plan to fire...{The space station has antimatter weapons. \NWe will fire the missiles.}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.45,0:53:37.45,Default,Italics,0,0,0,,...to destroy the meteorite.{And destroy the meteorite.}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.12,0:53:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be that this was \Nthe plan from the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.18,0:53:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The organization wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.64,0:54:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan moves into its second stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.25,0:54:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We pretended to bring a comet.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.01,0:54:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And we brought the meteorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.01,0:54:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore we pretend \Nto destroy the meteorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.66,0:54:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We hit it with missiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.68,0:54:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you believe in an afterlife{the next world}?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.26,0:54:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're going to be destroyed either way...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.18,0:54:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...then humanity can only live on in the Worms.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.02,0:54:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.88,0:54:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Jacob received a ladder to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.64,0:54:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps that ladder, is all we have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.89,0:54:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems we have a rat listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.02,0:55:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A present to celebrate your marriage from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.18,0:55:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This... is my mother's...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.82,0:55:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also a memento of my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.46,0:55:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.17,0:56:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had a brother, I'd want him\N to try my cooking, just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.09,0:56:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And then... I'd want him to say it tastes good.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.48,0:56:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... hurry and get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.96,0:56:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then make me a feast.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.09,0:56:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,However... it better not taste bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.74,0:56:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.81,0:57:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you two are together...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.94,0:57:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Through rich times. Through poor times.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.26,0:57:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You stay close. Living to \Nhelp and support each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.93,0:57:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you swear to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.98,0:57:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.97,0:57:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.36,0:57:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.66,0:59:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.66,0:59:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...were deceived by ZECT.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.21,0:59:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,ZECT... has joined with the Worms.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.86,0:59:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.10,0:59:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...can only...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.61,0:59:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...rely on you now...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.68,1:01:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You going?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.21,1:01:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to come.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.81,1:01:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Your fight...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.60,1:01:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...is my fight.
