Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.53,1:02:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Lift off.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.73,1:03:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Add to the color of my rose.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.80,1:03:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The red blood of a traitor \Nand your tears of humiliation.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.89,1:03:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform.
