Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.72,1:03:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Clock Up.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.17,1:03:49.02,Belt,,0,0,0,,CLOCK UP
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.16,1:03:50.62,Belt,,0,0,0,,HYPER CLOCK UP
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.69,1:04:03.48,Belt,,0,0,0,,HYPER CLOCK OVER
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.65,1:04:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He's faster than normal Clock Up.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.25,1:04:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Gravity device? How boring.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.59,1:04:28.06,Belt,,0,0,0,,HYPER CLOCK UP
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.29,1:04:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Gravity cannot beat my Hyper Clock Up.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.69,1:04:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your goal from the beginning\N was this Hyper Zecter, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.72,1:05:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,To make me appear you made \Nthe Riders wipe each other out.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.20,1:05:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you just waited for me to appear.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.94,1:05:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it's no use. The cradle \Ncarrying the Worm eggs is already here.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.49,1:05:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Worm eggs?!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.12,1:05:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The meteorite... is a cradle \Nfor carrying dormant Worms?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.02,1:05:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The missile exists to awaken them?!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.20,1:05:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the kiss from a prince?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.05,1:05:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.00,1:05:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, an overwhelming number of\N Worms are ready to destroy humanity.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.30,1:05:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're okay with that?!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.08,1:05:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Letting the Worms take Earth?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.82,1:05:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it's the Worms or\N the humans, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.66,1:05:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who finds the rose is the\N strongest and most beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.89,1:05:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I fight just for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.09,1:06:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A rose means "love".
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.27,1:06:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Scatter with my love.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.49,1:06:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... Kick!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.24,1:06:19.58,Belt,,0,0,0,,MAXIMUM RIDER POWER
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.10,1:06:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.17,1:06:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I was able...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.74,1:06:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.12,1:06:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.44,1:07:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's thanks to you...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.89,1:07:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiyori...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.58,1:07:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
