Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.52,1:15:26.04,Show Song Font english KABUTO,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}My boots are worn from all this walking
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.04,1:15:32.62,Show Song Font english KABUTO,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm on the brink of despair
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.62,1:15:45.50,Show Song Font english KABUTO,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}When I close my eyes, I see a faint glimmer of your smile{I close my eyes, and your face appears, so faintly}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.18,1:15:52.64,Show Song Font english KABUTO,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We used to run on the beach
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.64,1:15:59.22,Show Song Font english KABUTO,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}With our arms wrapped around each other,\N as we faced the setting sun{And have our arms around each other as we watch the sunset}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.22,1:16:14.33,Show Song Font english KABUTO,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Such calm, ordinary days are what make me happy
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.68,1:16:28.30,Show Song Font english KABUTO,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Storms may come, the wind may hurl me about, and I may be hurt
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.30,1:16:32.70,Show Song Font english KABUTO,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Even then, I wish to keep this love of mine
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.70,1:16:41.04,Show Song Font english KABUTO,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's gonna be alright, I'll always be by your side
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.05,1:16:53.48,Show Song Font english KABUTO,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No matter how far apart we are, we both share this One World
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.48,1:17:01.56,Show Song Font english KABUTO,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Even if I turn my back to destiny, \Nover great distances, going to a distant time
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.56,1:17:05.98,Show Song Font english KABUTO,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}There is a place I want to come home to
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.98,1:17:13.46,Show Song Font english KABUTO,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'll never leave this place for anything in the entire universe
